definitions.definition: An edible plant ( Brassica oleracea var. capitata ) having a head of green leaves .

subdefinitions.definition: ( by extension ) Any of various cultivars of the species Brassica oleracea .

definitions.definition: ( uncountable , vegetable ) The leaves of this plant eaten as a vegetable .
( countable , offensive ) A person with severely reduced mental capacities due to brain damage .
examples: After the car crash, he became a cabbage .

definitions.definition: Used as a term of endearment.
( uncountable , slang ) Marijuana leaf, the part that is not smoked but from which cannabutter can be extracted.
A terminal bud of certain palm trees , used for food.
A cabbage palmetto ( Sabal palmetto ), a palm of the southeastern US coasts and nearby islands.
( slang , African-American Vernacular ) A human head.
